{"tid":1250221,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下一個焦點：警方砌生豬肉","createTime":"2019-06-22T04:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T02:25:40.000Z","uid":264780,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8796ae86ff9cefcfeeecc9a671c3de2fc28a0bfb","tid":1250221,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"大家都見到警方<span style=\"font-size: large;\">故意阻住救援，再砌示威者生豬肉</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1249709/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1249709/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立調查，警隊改革</span>又係幾個訴求入面，容易得到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最大支持</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1247598/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1247598/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n連國際特赦組織都出埋聲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1247785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1247785/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n又警方最驚嘅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1244391/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1244391/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n所以個焦點可以放喺警方<span style=\"color: red;\">誣陷示威者</span>上面，配合<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立調查，警隊改革</span>個主旋律<br />\n<br />\n另外見到大家發起搵就近嘅港鐡站做新目標<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1247726/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1247726/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n其實喺港鐡站，尤其喺多大陸人嘅上水沙田之類，可以集中焦點文宣喺<span style=\"color: red;\">警方砌示威者生豬肉</span>上面<br />\n<br />\n一嚟可以清一清 CCTVB 嘅不實報到<br />\n二嚟，大陸人對公安砌生豬肉係好易明白嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成日大陸有大型暴動就係因為公安砌生豬肉</span><br />\n講呢個 Point 去反攻大陸，中共仲驚過你<br />\n話唔定呢排邊條村又有被自殺事件發生緊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d8b91d131f90f392e5a51c04e5b8fd11242128","tid":1250221,"uid":213142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-2